<paragraph id="84B903E5EB443E0820A7B26CA08C9C29" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Rostans Enzian</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="17111788724D2337EA0D8B9104440150" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" type="description">
<paragraph id="20ACBF8C5FFD03DB29062A84BB3C18CC" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="A65BF23CBB11A7579928893CFCAF70EF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
Untere 
<normalizedToken id="E4A4B88AE74FE5FBA388A8E5546FEDFF" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
am Stengel oft 
<normalizedToken id="179FF0B15A4D2DB04CA8C6D87165767D" originalValue="gedrängt" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">gedraengt</normalizedToken>
, aber nicht in einer Rosette
</emphasis>
, schmal oval, meist 
<normalizedToken id="82157A3695CCA741478CCED8C9E6448A" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">+/-</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="D184289D368A1D543C419C0CD6499EB5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">stumpf</emphasis>
, etwa in der Mitte am breitesten, 
<emphasis id="47F0647E4359FA8E0F6B8884934AF2CD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="87AEF4D3ADE430A75F87413DD7174D80" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">4mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
, bis 3 cm lang, 
<emphasis id="789604AC23729E3B7C11D2F4C526F1DE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
bedeutend 
<normalizedToken id="81401B9CE17E95B3D1BB6A4156276414" originalValue="größer" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">groesser</normalizedToken>
als die obern
</emphasis>
, matt, weich. 
<emphasis id="3A3869903F0B7B9326464FBF7AB092E9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Kelch 1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="D45A78ED01020EFF05D33F40D87DEBD8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
15 mm 
<normalizedToken id="A6B0140C5CFAD34D72A6575783600DD4" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">ueber</normalizedToken>
dem obersten Stengelblattpaar
</emphasis>
, an den Kanten kaum 
<normalizedToken id="BB8FED8CC3403DEF3FAD84AF5C327F09" originalValue="geflügelt" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">gefluegelt</normalizedToken>
, ⅔- 
<normalizedToken id="BFCC65042600C0107D567AFCF1694229" originalValue="¾" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">3/4</normalizedToken>
so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="6A43940E78DB7FA707780379D62C6824" originalValue="Kronröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Kronroehre</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="4D0CA9B5915D97EF9264A74F65F7C343" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">bis auf</emphasis>
⅔- 
<normalizedToken id="050D7CC26609056B8C558244D431B117" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="E7D8276EE6FEF5F8C7E35892384B88BA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
der 
<normalizedToken id="A2FB717A5069118F2B28E0DC00449B32" originalValue="Länge" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Laenge</normalizedToken>
5teilig, 
<normalizedToken id="BB26C7ACE43D74BB8EB5917FD4A7DC1D" originalValue="gepreßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">gepresst</normalizedToken>
3
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="7CDB823A6DEF81E08E9C26C8826238DC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">4 mm breit.</emphasis>
Krone mit 1,8-2,5 cm langer 
<normalizedToken id="BB93459CD03162DA4F0E85D0F0105CE9" originalValue="Röhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Roehre</normalizedToken>
. - 
<normalizedToken id="AF6D5BCC21DF10971D6595F97D892211" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5CF6FDFE8C9CFAA165A3295F6DE033C3" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="358CA93734E1F4D1ABA312A425177C9F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="0A63C271F063E596169814F71433CDFD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">30:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Val Queyras (Favarger 1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FF4C01197526CB83A490713E277FD125" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="E59F511FF89D151A4B1A71BD6C20BA55" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Feuchte Wiesen, 
<normalizedToken id="4B0A1FE7EBA2F1FE214C7B9E6B4D65E1" originalValue="Bachränder" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Bachraender</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="930E51CC9D3939092EAFDC436ACB8005" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="A575700F1358BAECA1EEBE3C5B821835" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<pageBreakToken id="1712F95056345D59013A7041C04B8907" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Verbreitung</pageBreakToken>
. Westalpen-Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Hautes Alpes, Basses Alpes, Piemont. - Im Gebiet nicht sicher nachgewiesen, Aostatal (?). Angaben aus dem Wallis und Tessin beziehen sich auf andere Arten (vgl. Kunz 1940).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="35842101BFC026D75DC16E9F4045EDF7" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">
<emphasis id="09DDB4699E6977C6B2B56DEAE96178AC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="39624E189F3909325FB5FBE560E3D782" originalValue="Über" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">Ueber</normalizedToken>
die Morphologie von 
<taxonomicName id="A6BC7AFE00EAEE7B1D9C29F06108876E" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gentianaceae" genus="Gentiana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rostanii">
<emphasis id="D955F66C8693C2E9E4061A75EC255B91" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">G. Rostanii</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
s. Kunz (1970), wo auf die nahe Verwandtschaft zu 
<taxonomicName id="7BCBACBE7DF960C2F50D391F8ED1BD09" authority="Nr." authorityName="Nr." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gentianaceae" genus="Gentiana" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="null" pageNumber="30" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bavarica">
<emphasis id="B58EC67FF2AFFB6FAC155BD1E3FE25D5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="30">G. bavarica</emphasis>
Nr.
</taxonomicName>
10f hingewiesen wird.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
